		<descript>
			<langdata>eng</langdata>
			<abstract>This is a scanned version of the paper map entitled: California.  The original map is on two sheets, one each for the upper and lower halves of California.  The map was scanned at 300 dots per inch and is in the TIFF format.</abstract>
			<purpose>Scanned maps may be used for a variety of purposes.   This dataset contains two images, one for each original map sheet. The images may be used in a GIS..</purpose>
